  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To confirm the benefit of endoscopic resection under fluorescence and blue light of high
      grade non-muscle invasive bladder tumor, and verifying if the second endoscopic resection
      recommended nowadays can be deleted.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
